  sales force is a software that allows us to manage all our customers details (C.R.M) at one place for other companies.
  sales force makes the projects that gives companies a complete view about their customers so they can build deeper relationships
  helps other companies get knowledge about how to maximize the ROI by gathering all the data collected by that company about their custoners at oneplace and sorthing and analysing it dowm efficiently.
